      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">Introduction to Vedic Astrology</h2>
      
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        Vedic Astrology studies the positions of the planets, Moon, Sun, and fixed stars at the time of a person's birth. This birth chart, called a kundli, helps an astrologer read patterns about career, relationships, health, and spiritual growth.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
