      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        The practical approach of Vedic Astrology, combined with its spiritual foundation, makes it relevant even in modern times. It provides a framework for understanding life's challenges and opportunities, offering hope and direction when needed most.
      </p>

